{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/titre1_english.png?t=1710756356\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/testgif2.gif?t=1710756356\" /><br><br>Decarnation plunges you into a haunting, dreamlike adventure where reality and fantasy become one. Inspired by some of the most influential surrealist works (Silent Hill, the original tale of Alice in Wonderland, films by David Lynch and Satoshi Kon...), allow yourself to be swept away by an intense and mesmerising story, oscillating between dreams and nightmares.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/titre2_english.png?t=1710756356\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/gif1test2.gif?t=1710756356\" /><br><br>Gloria is a cabaret dancer at the end of her rope. As her career, relationships and self-esteem begin to deteriorate, a mysterious patron makes her an offer she couldn\u2019t possibly refuse. Will this event mark the end of her recent struggles , or the beginning of her descent into hell? <br>Decarnation is a story of survival, where monsters and nightmares weave themselves into the fabric of everyday life. Get ready for a poignant and captivating adventure!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/titre3_english.png?t=1710756356\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/gif2test3.gif?t=1710756356\" /><br><br>With a wide variety of mini-games, Decarnation expertly brings together the classic elements of horror and adventure games, where each challenge requires consideration, responsiveness and coordination. Solve cryptic riddles, confront ominous enemies and explore a bewildering world...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/titre4_english.png?t=1710756356\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1672310/extras/gif3test.gif?t=1710756356\" /><br><br>Decarnation's R\u00eave and Cauchemar soundtracks feature contributions from numerous artists, including the renowned composer <strong>Akira Yamaoka</strong> (Silent Hill) whose works blend horror and the paranormal, breathing life into this nightmarish tale.<br><br><i>&quot;I'm delighted to have been able to take part in the development of Decarnation [...] I've developed a special bond with this game.</i><br><br>Numerous references and inspirations from cult horror works have shaped the world of Decarnation - can you spot them all?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Dancer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/43fb83b4647282ebc56e8a11b6938d8e2841bce0.jpg"},{"name":"The Captive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/a37031a8044f7c023d2c70628a68a739e6bccafc.jpg"},{"name":"The Kid","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/ccb4e8583de6294d13562aa648bd258f1c649de2.jpg"},{"name":"The Princess","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/4f90fb9a17f4d4970b7288f020c0a7099f9c2e5a.jpg"},{"name":"The Phoenix","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/6c68f7cff574c017558d47dd6db940988f4b170f.jpg"},{"name":"Gloria","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/31b6ae94c28428bad5986070d0b3c03e630cff74.jpg"},{"name":"Checkmate","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1672310/98e381bab41caca5fa4c2a9d3a1a064550a9e9c5.jpg"},{"name":"Stu